snippet.title: CodeBreakers | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
We are super excited to present the trailer of our first video game, Codebreakers VR. 

It's a Sci-fi Arcade VR Shooter where frenetic music and intense battles will put your skills to the test.

--
We hope you like it as much as we do! 
#indiegame #firstgame #vr #futuristic #shooter #meta #oculus
